      "source": "https://thegabber.com/lealmans-agricultural-history/"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "Historically, Lealman spanned from Pinellas Park and Sawgrass Lake westward through Kenneth City toward Cross Bayou.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
