      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://thegabber.com/lealmans-agricultural-history/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The arrival of regular railroad service in the early 1900s fueled the growth of farms and citrus groves across the area.",
